{{Quote|You think we are weak and stupid. But the Ithorian Supremacy League will prove you all wrong.|translated=1|Lasavvou|<ref name="Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref>}}
The '''Ithorian Supremacy League''' was mentioned by [[Lasavvou|Lassavou]] on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]], in the [[Nar Shaddaa Docks|Docks sector]]. His accidental mention of it, and his subsequent attempt to cover it up, leads to speculation that it was a secret organization formed to attack perceived views of [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]] weakness.

